{"tid":1609644,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"罷工搞咁急點搞得切呀 下次宣傳多D先啦","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T16:02:50.000Z","uid":33775,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f269501c9e9b33e211f99f4a743ead36d0172aa2","tid":1609644,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrCZrRf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrCZrRf.jpg&h=49cead2e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再講呢D我屌晒你地老母呀<br />\n人地真係擋左啦<br />\n咁罷工肯成真未?<br />\n宣傳? 又射唔到波? 份工好緊要? <br />\n會唔會夠人地條命緊要?<br />\n唔該你地唔好再為自己垃圾搵借口 <br />\n你唔敢上去打狗我都唔怪 而家叫你罷工都多多理由</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f943fe9004f49c6dc96c5478a132a9476d63acd6","tid":1609644,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"經過今日 殺警都唔係問題 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609207</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"051f97e5c0a1475ead86efc3908d426df728b1af","tid":1609644,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b4cf97b0a20b4e23e948c734bf58b6a98032b5","tid":1609644,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:12:31.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n義士既血不能白流 <br />\n絕對唔撚可以就咁算"},{"pid":"9c7c5db3e577333a6f188e220148d16cc6e362ea","tid":1609644,"uid":54977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:13:20.000Z","msg":"差啲想屌你 香港人咁撚善忘 過埋今晚都唔記得"},{"pid":"8cd2883d327bc97f9002dfa13ec52da106293507","tid":1609644,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:15:00.000Z","msg":"仲有堆被罷工既on9唔該屌撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edfd8